sudokuGame.Individual

    • Uses of Individual in sudokuGame

      Subclasses of Individual in sudokuGame 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  BoardIndividual
      BoardIndividual is representing the player that trying to solve the sudoku board, this class is extend Individual abstract class and implement the abstract method evaluate that call play method that will try to solve the sudoku board according to the tree-based GP, and return the fitness of the BoardIndividual.

      Individual Population.getBest()
      Return the best player (individual), the best player is the one with the lowest fitness.
      private Individual Evolution.getBest()
      Gets the best player (individual) that have lowest fitness, player with lowest fitness is the player that have the lowest amount of empty cells before he could NOT progress without having conflicts in the board solution.
      Individual Population.getWorst()
      Return the worst player (individual), the worst player is the one with the highest fitness.
      private Individual Evolution.getWorst()
      Gets the worst player (individual) that have highest fitness, player with highest fitness is the player that have the highest amount of empty cells before he could NOT progress without having conflicts in the board solution (a kind of loser).
